channel.title: [vid] Me and some friends really hammered
channel.description:
Yeah well anyways we had today off, so we got really drunk earlier and did stupid stupid things. I'm bored right now so I uploaded the vid. It's really random and pointless. I just took some of our clips and put them together. I guess this is a glimpse of my everyday life :P I won't tell you who I am in this video, figure it out yourself ;)
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fHYqBSIpP3Y
Btw, yes that is a TV that falls out of the car window.
edit: Alright I'll tell you I'm the most idiotic one there. The one smashing beer bottles and stuff. We didn't film too much, I should buy myself a good camera and show you guys some crazy shit we do sometimes.
